Source: bongosec-indexer
Section: admin
Priority: extra
Maintainer: Bongosec, Inc <info@bongosec.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>=9)
Standards-Version: 4.0.0
Homepage: https://www.bongosec.com

Package: bongosec-indexer
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, debconf, adduser, procps
Description: Bongosec indexer is a near real-time full-text search and analytics engine that gathers security-related data into one platform.
 This Bongosec central component indexes and stores alerts generated by the Bongosec server.
 Bongosec indexer can be configured as a single-node or multi-node cluster, providing scalability and high availability.
 Documentation can be found at https://documentation.bongosec.com/current/getting-started/components/bongosec-indexer.html
